# Stjarndag — Roadmap Task Structure

Follow `docs/prompt-roadmap-förbättringar.md` (rev 5) exactly.

## Task 1 — Auth + Onboarding
- Chunk-read `src/routes/auth.js` (register/Apple sections)
- Chunk-read `src/routes/onboarding.js`
- **Do NOT touch the rest of auth.js**

## Tasks 2–3 — New feature files
- New code goes in `public/js/dashboard-cta.js` and/or `public/js/dashboard-share.js`
- Minimal diff in `dashboard.js` (add `<script>` tag + init call only)
- No large-file rewrites

## Task 4 — Win-back scheduler
- New file: `src/lib/win-back-scheduler.js`
- Migration file for DB changes
- Email template in `src/lib/email.js` via grep — do not read entire email.js

## Task 5 — Child settings
- `public/js/child-settings.js` — chunk-read only
- `public/js/child-dashboard.js` — chunk-read only

## Required in every PR

1. **Feature slugs** — add to `scripts/seed-features.js` in the same PR
2. **SW cache bump** — bump `CACHE_NAME` in `public/sw.js` on any frontend change
3. **Commit** — only on explicit user request

## ❌/✅ Examples

❌ Wrong:
```
read src/routes/auth.js  (full auth.js is ~16k tokens)
```

✅ Correct:
```
grep "register|appleSignup" src/routes/auth.js
read src/routes/auth.js offset=200 limit=100
```